snippet.title: SIFU - Official Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
This new SIFU gameplay trailer features intense hand-to-hand combat at a location named The Club and a flashy stand-off focusing on a new fighter. SIFU is coming soon to PS4, PS5, and PC via the Epic Games Store.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
